$ bundle install --local --standalone

Install imgkit's wkhtmltoimage at /usr/local/bin

$ bundle exec imgkit --install-wkhtmltoimage


Airplay Icon:
http://images.apple.com/ipad/features/airplay/images/airplay_icon.jpg

Cron jobs for Sharp Aquous displays:
  # Turn screens on at 9:30am local time Monday - Friday
  30 9 * * 1-5   bin/aquous.rb --quiet --arp en3 --on
  # Turn screens off at 6:30pm local time every day
  30 18 * * *    bin/aquous.rb --quiet --arp en3 --off
